8:T3c35,<p>Just as the whispers of bygone souls echo in Edgar Allan Poe&#8217;s tales, <strong>abandoned asylums</strong> offer a haunting glimpse into the past. Each location, from the eerie corridors of Eastern State Penitentiary to the chilling halls of the Trans-Allegheny Lunatic Asylum, tells a story of despair and intrigue. You might find yourself captivated by the <strong>ghostly legends</strong> that linger in the air. Discover what awaits those brave enough to explore these <strong>spine-tingling sites</strong>.</p>
